Title: An Act Changing the Name of Kulukipus Primary School in the Municipality of Jose Abad Santos, Province of Davao Del Sur, to Rolando Pardenas Primary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 761
An Act Changing the Name of Kulukipus Primary School in the Municipality of Jose Abad Santos, Province of Davao Del Sur, to Rolando Pardenas Primary School
Section 1. The name of Kulukipus Primary School in the Municipality of Jose Abad Santos, Province of Davao del Sur, is changed to Rolando Pardenas Primary School.1avvphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 13, 1984
